(27295, 'Soozy intimate wash 250 ml', 'سوزي غسول مهبلي 250 مل', '49', '95', 'Chlorhexidine 0.1%+aloe vera+chamomile+green tea ext.+thyme+malva sylvestris+menthol+tea tree oil+rose', 'Egyptian co. for cosmetics > integra pharm', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', 'غسول مهبلي لتقليل فرص الاصابة بالعدوي', 'Vaginal care', '250 ml', 'Chlorhexidine is available over-the-counter in various formulations (e.g. solution, sponge, cloth, swab) as a topical antiseptic to sanitize prior to surgeries and/or medical procedures.[L11518,L11521,L11527,L11533] Dental formulations, available by prescription only, include an oral rinse indicated for the treatment of gingivitis[L11512] and a slow-release "chip" which is inserted into periodontal pockets and is indicated for the reduction of pocket depth in adult patients with periodontitis as an adjunct therapy to dental scaling and root planing procedures.[L11536]', '', '', 984, '2024-10-03', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
