(24021, 'Olmesab 10 mg 20 f.c. tabs.', 'اولميساب 10مجم 20 اقراص', '', '18', 'Olmesartan', 'Sabaa > activa therapeutics', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Antihypertensive.angiotensin blocker', '10 mg', 'Olmesartan is indicated for the treatment of hypertension either alone or in combination with other antihypertensive agents.[F4709,F4712,A173869] 
